<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The Pacific Ocean is to the west of the wester=
n part of the US. The US has like a zillion banks, most of them pretty loca=
l. Often they have blandly geographical names. If you are a bank in the wes=
tern part of the US, sorta near the ocean, your name might well include the=
 words=C2=A0=E2=80=9CPacific=E2=80=9D or =E2=80=9Cwest=E2=80=9D or both. Th=
e western part of the US is large and has a lot of coastline, and also a lo=
t of banks, so it should not be surprising that there is both a =E2=80=9CPa=
cific West Bancorp=E2=80=9D (the holding company for Pacific West=C2=A0Bank=
) and a =E2=80=9CPacWest Bancorp=E2=80=9D (the holding company for Pacific =
West<em>ern</em> Bank), or that they are entirely different banks. PacWest =
Bancorp=E2=80=99s stock has had a wild ride=C2=A0in recent days. Pacific We=
st Bancorp=E2=80=99s stock has not. <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergb=
usiness.com/click/31392592.261430/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL=
2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDUtMDQvcGFjaWZpYy13ZXN0LWJhbmNvcnAtc2Vla3MtdG8tYXZvaWQt=
YS1jYXNlLW9mLW1pc3Rha2VuLWlkZW50aXR5P2NtcGlkPUJCRDA1MDUyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV=
0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDUwNSZ1dG=
1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB92cf584c" itemprop=3D=
"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0000=
00; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bott=
om-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">It =
would like to keep it that way</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Pacific West Bancorp, a small lender based out=
side Portland, Oregon, is seeking to distance itself from a California comp=
any with a similar moniker,=C2=A0PacWest Bancorp, whose shares have plummet=
ed amid the recent regional-banking turmoil.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CRecent local and national news report=
s have highlighted the financial difficulties of a bank with a similar name=
 in California, leading to concerns that PWB may also be facing similar cha=
llenges,=E2=80=9D West Linn, Oregon-based Pacific West Bancorp said in a=C2=
=A0statement=C2=A0Thursday. =E2=80=9CHowever, PWB wants to make it clear th=
at it is a separate entity with no affiliation to the California-based bank=
.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The company with a similar name, Beverly Hills=
-based PacWest Bancorp, has sought to calm its own investors, reporting tha=
t core deposits have increased since March and confirming it=E2=80=99s in t=
alks with several potential investors after a stock rout made it the new fo=
cal point of concern over the health of US regional lenders. Still, its sha=
res plunged as much as 61% Thursday, and are down more than 85% this year.<=
/p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I once=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloom=
bergbusiness.com/click/31392592.261430/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9tYXR0X2xl=
dmluZS9zdGF0dXMvMTY0MTgyMDU0NDc1NTQ2MjE0NA/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB24e48ab=
a" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=
=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: =
1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;">joked on Twitter</a> that the =E2=80=9Cbiggest risk to the US =
banking system is there are 4000 banks and they all have like six names.=E2=
=80=9D That was in response to a <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/31392592.261430/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2Fy=
dGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDMtMzEvcmVwdWJsaWMtZmlyc3QtaXMtbm90LWZpcnN0LXJlcHVibGljLWJ=
1dC10cnktdGVsbGluZy10cmFkZXJzP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA1MDUyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZW=
RpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDUwNSZ1dG1fY2Ftc=
GFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBdef708ff" itemprop=3D"StoryL=
ink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; tex=
t-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-colo=
r: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  Bloomber=
g News story about Republic First Bancorp</a>, which put out a statement sa=
ying that it was not First Republic Bank. Easy mistake to make! First Repub=
