<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">No, but, I mean, I can see <a href=3D"https://=
link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31392592.261430/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqL=
mNvbS9hcnRpY2xlcy9jb2luYmFzZS10cmllcy1ub3ZlbC1kZWZlbnNlLWluLXNlYy1maWdodC00=
